HTML :
<input type="text" id="taskInput"> → Input field for tasks
<button id="addTask"> → Button to add tasks
<ul id="taskList"> → List container for tasks

CSS :
border-radius: 5px; → Styles buttons and input fields
hover { background-color: lightgray; } → Changes button color on hover
text-decoration: line-through; → Crosses out completed tasks

JavaScript :
getElementById("taskInput") → Gets user input
createElement("li") → Creates a new list item
appendChild(taskItem) → Adds the task to the list
removeChild(taskItem) → Deletes a task when clicked
